task.summary: Added Oracle function to select random process according to their merit. Added function to add the list of processes to the oracle and normalise their wieghts to compute the probability distribution of the list. Defined the condition for oracle to fire its transitions between its two states.

Edited Block Constructor: 1) Added genesis block case 2) Cleaned up parameter input 3) Added simple block hash system. Added Blocktree initialisation using genesis block and its hash. Implemented Block Automata, including transitions and conditions. Added Basic execution script and template input XML File.
Added main section of the program to run simulation. Fixing bugs. Contains issue with the block automaton and creation that needs to be fixed.

Added message box between oracle and blocktree to identify where the latest update is coming from. Fixed issues with the process automaton and oracle automaton for the creation and reception of pending blocks. TODO: identify fix for the block automata, including the simulate transit of blocks among the processes.
Clunky Fix for Block Automaton Issue with independently conditions. Needs refining.
Clunky Fix for Block Automaton Issue with independently conditions. Needs refining.

Created Connection class to schedule block arrivals. Added basic scheduler to place new pending blocks in one of the established process Connections. Current Implementation extracts similar to results to those found in the paper.

Created Connection class to schedule block arrivals. Added basic scheduler to place new pending blocks in one of the established process Connections. Current Implementation extracts similar to results to those found in the paper.
Added Block Size equation. Added File Output for dumping simulation results.

Added transaction properties to blocks: - Blocks now contain a number of transactions which impact the size of the block (transaction rate and size). - The random numbers generated in the system were modified to be constrained in a tighter, more realistic range. - The average block size was added as an indicator at the end of a simulation
Added script to read session dumps, Added directed file output to required folder, Minor code cleanup
